                    <zone forceUpdate='true' h='9875' id='38' type-v2='text' w='66300' x='33300' y='500'>
                      <formatted-text>
                        <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='8'>*Data in this report was pulled out of SO99 on 9/14/2021 and represents Dealer Orders  through 9/11/2021. This data does not include DSS orders that have not been uploaded to SAP.</run>
                        <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                        <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='8'>*This report includes all styles from &quot;2021 July Core&quot;, &quot;2022 Spring&quot;, &quot;2022 Summer,  &quot;2021 Winter Chase&quot;, and &quot;2021 Fall Chase&quot;  with Introduction Status  &quot;New&quot; in Flex PLM.</run>
                        <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                        <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='8'>*</run>
                        <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='8'>Order Quantity</run>
                        <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='8'>Æ </run>
                        <run fontsize='8'>represents orders placed by dealers at the regional DCs. This data does not account for Back Orders or Cancelations, thus they will still be included in the data.</run>
                        <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                        <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='8'>*Order $ (USD)</run>
                        <run fontsize='8'> represents Order Quantity out of SO99 priced at U.S. Dealer Net pulled from SAP.</run>
                      </formatted-text>
                      <zone-style>
                        <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                        <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                        <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
                        <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                        <format attr='background-color' value='#d4d4d4' />
